Surface morphology of MP120-MP124 films, as measured by AFM, is shown in Fig. 7a–e. The uniformed growth throughout the sample area along with scattered voids is observed when HFR is low. The estimated RMS surface roughness (dRMS\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
